# vanity-address — session context

**Read first:** [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) for full project memory, release checklist, and pending work.

## Quick facts

- Rust workspace: `vanity-core` (engine) + `vanity-address` (CLI) + `vanity-app` (Tauri desktop)
- **v0.3.6** on crates.io; chain logic only in `vanity-core`
- Publish order: `vanity-core` then `vanity-address` (no `#` on same shell line)
- Homebrew: `Formula/vanity-address.rb` + scripts; tap `yudizaxay/tap` — users need `brew trust yudizaxay/tap` on Homebrew 6+
- Formula must use `std_cargo_args` (not `std_cargo_install_args`)
- npm: `npm/vanity-address` + platform pkgs; `./scripts/prepare-npm.sh` then `./scripts/publish-npm.sh`
- Windows CLI: `terminal.rs` Press-only keys; `menu.rs` crossterm clear
- crates.io README needs absolute GitHub/raw URLs for images and links

## Before releases

`make check-ci` → version bump all packages → `CHANGELOG.md` → Homebrew formula → tag → `cargo publish` → sync Homebrew tap → `prepare-npm` + `publish-npm`

